### Finance API Test Examples
### Use com VS Code REST Client extension ou Postman/Insomnia

### 1. REGISTRO DE USUÁRIO
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 2. LOGIN
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. CRIAR BANCO (se necessário)
POST http://localhost:8080/banks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Banco do Brasil",
  "code": "001"
}

### 4. CRIAR CONTA
POST http://localhost:8080/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "bankId": 1,
  "name": "Conta Corrente Principal",
  "type": "CHECKING",
  "balance": 1000.00
}

### 5. LISTAR CONTAS
GET http://localhost:8080/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. CRIAR TRANSAÇÃO - RECEITA
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "accountId": 1,
  "name": "Salário",
  "category": "SALARY",
  "type": "INCOME",
  "amount": 3000.00
}

### 7. CRIAR TRANSAÇÃO - DESPESA
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "accountId": 1,
  "name": "Compra no supermercado",
  "category": "FOOD",
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "amount": 150.50
}

### 8. ATUALIZAR CONTA
PATCH http://localhost:8080/accounts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Conta Corrente Atualizada"
}

### 9. DELETAR CONTA
DELETE http://localhost:8080/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. DOCUMENTAÇÃO SWAGGER
GET http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html

### 11. API DOCS JSON
GET http://localhost:8080/v3/api-docs

### Variáveis para usar (substitua {{token}} pelo JWT retornado no login)
# token = seu_jwt_token_aqui 